[It is of concern that 6 of the cases in Taiwan had no clear source of infection, especially when less than 1% of the population is immunized. The rise in cases centered around a hotel used to quarantine pilots is particularly troublesome. This is a situation where rapid tests could be very effective. - Mod.LK]

